message:
Hi guys 
recently i went to interviews as android developer. I noticed something, so i want to ask this.

What are the skills -apart from the technical skills- that a 3 years of exp developer/software eng should have?  or more like a generic tech-skills that is not android/ios/?? related.

data.message: Basics of computer science,data structures and algorithms, source control

Read the art of unit testing and code complete. Plus be calm, collected and capable of planning, saying no, thinking methodically. Being productive, but in the right way, not just working long hours, focused productivity. No when to rest and when to work and how to plan and manage your time.
